#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "A complete free replacement for DOOM II — 32 levels with the Super Shotgun. Compatible with community PWAD mods."
msgstr "Un reemplazo completo gratuito para DOOM II — 32 niveles con el Super Shotgun. Compatible con mods comunitarios PWAD."

